        ----
        
        - tested under python2.7
        - bumped sqlalchemy and celery versions
        
        fixes
        -----
        
        - fixed #59 missing graph.js
        - fixed repo_size crash when repository had broken symlinks
        - fixed python2.5 crashes.
        
        
        1.0.1 (**2010-11-10**)
